2. CUSTOMIZATION OPTIONS:
   - Border radius: Change "16px" in .rounded-image-wrapper
   - Shadow intensity: Adjust rgba values in box-shadow
   - Grid gap: Change "80px" in .recibo-content-grid
   - Animation timing: Modify values in the script section

3. ELEMENTOR SETTINGS:
   - Set widget width to "Full Width"
   - Remove any widget margins
   - If using container, set to "Boxed" or "Full Width"

4. PERFORMANCE TIPS:
   - Optimize image (use WebP format if possible)
   - Consider lazy loading for below-fold placement
